      "message": "The Build proto has critical as a Trinary to allow for UNSET (http://cs/github/luci/luci-go/buildbucket/proto/build.proto?l\u003d170\u0026rcl\u003d67da9c91fe05ef8b1257caa6ccdc99da6e05b171). Should we match that here?\n\nFor context on this: Will this field be passed directly to the field on the Build proto?",
